TAG_HIGHWAY

public static final java.lang.String TAG_HIGHWAY
"highway" denotes general type or road. Valid values on ways:
  • "motorway"
  • "motorway_link"
  • "motorway_junction"
  • "trunk"
  • "trunk_link"
  • "primary"
  • "primary_link"
  • "secondary"
  • "tertiary"
  • "unclassified"
  • "track"
  • "residential"
  • "footway"
  • "cycleway"
Valid values on nodes:
  • "mini_roundabout"
  • "stop"
  • "traffic_signals"
  • "crossing"
  • "toll_booth"
  • "incline"
  • "incline_steep"
  • "ford"
  • "bus_stop"
